#}

{# The subject line. #}
{%- block subject -%}{%- autoescape false -%}
Welcome to Noth American Challenger! Please confirm your email.
{%- endautoescape -%}{%- endblock -%}

{# The plain text message. #}
{%- block body_text -%}{%- autoescape false -%}
Hello,


Thank you for registering for a Metamoris account.

In order to activate your account, please follow the link below:
{{ confirmationUrl }}


Regards,

- Metamoris Team
If you have any questions please email us at info@metamoris.com Thank you, now go train!

-Metamoris Team

{%- endautoescape -%}{%- endblock -%}

